<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Nominate an induction tutor
      for <%= @nominate_induction_tutor_form.school.name %></h1>

    <p class="govuk-body">Your induction tutor will use our online service to:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>choose how your school wants to run an induction for early career teachers</li>
      <li>complete some steps to set up a programme</li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>use the DfE accredited materials</li>
    </ul>
   <p class="govuk-body">They will also receive any future updates about the service.</p>
   <p class="govuk-body">Your induction tutor is someone at your school who usually manages statutory inductions for early career teachers. 
</p>
   <p class="govuk-body">They coordinate the training, support and assessment these new teachers receive. 
</p>
    <p class="govuk-body">If you think this is your role, you can nominate yourself. 
</p>
    <%= govuk_link_to "Continue", { action: :new }, class: 'govuk-button' %>
  </div>
</div>
